android.car.storagemonitoring

类 IoStatsEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.storagemonitoring.IoStatsEntry
  • 已过时。 
    use CarWatchdogManager and its related classes for I/O related tasks.

    @Deprecated
public final class IoStatsEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    uid_io stats about one user ID. Contains information about I/O activity that can be attributed to processes running on behalf of one user of the system, as collected by the kernel.

    • 字段详细资料

      • CREATOR

        public static final <any> CREATOR
        已过时。 

      • uid

        public final int uid
        已过时。 
        The user id that this object contains metrics for. In many cases this can be converted to a list of Java app packages installed on the device. In other cases, the user id can refer to either the kernel itself (uid 0), or low-level system services that are running entirely natively.

      • runtimeMillis

        public final long runtimeMillis
        已过时。 
        How long any process running on behalf of this user id running for, in milliseconds. This field is allowed to be an approximation and it does not provide any way to relate uptime to specific processes.

      • foreground

        public final IoStatsEntry.Metrics foreground
        已过时。 
        Statistics for apps running in foreground.

        public final IoStatsEntry.Metrics background
        已过时。 
        Statistics for apps running in background.

      • delta

        public IoStatsEntry delta(IoStatsEntry other)
        已过时。 
        Returns the difference between the values stored in this object vs. those stored in other. It is the same as doing a delta() on foreground and background, plus verifying that both objects refer to the same uid.

      • representsSameMetrics

        public boolean representsSameMetrics(UidIoRecord record)
        已过时。 
        Validates that this object contains the same I/O metrics as a UidIoStatsRecord. It matches UID, and I/O activity values, but ignores runtime.
